<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h4 id="html-snippet" class="html-title pt-4"># Snippets</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-7">
      <div class="input-group mt-4 mb-4">
        <div class="input-group-prepend">
          <label class="font-weight-bold input-group-text">Select snippet</label>
        </div>
        <select class="custom-select js-html-select box-shadow-none" data-id="Snippet">
          <optgroup class="text-primary" label="Easy">
            <option selected value="blockquote-1">Quote 1</option>
            <option value="blockquote-2">Quote 2</option>
            <option value="service-1">Service 1</option>
            <option value="service-2">Service 2</option>
            <option value="service-3">Service 3</option>
            <option value="js-video">HTML5 Video</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup class="text-success" label="Medium">
            <option value="card-member-1">Staff member 1</option>
            <option value="card-member-2">Staff member 2</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup class="text-danger" label="Hard">
            <option value="accordion-1">Accordion</option>
          </optgroup>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-7 col-left">
      <textarea id="htmlCode-Snippet" class="html-code">
        <blockquote class="blockquote blockquote-1 bg-white p-5 shadow rounded">
          <div class="blockquote-custom-icon bg-info shadow-sm"></div>
          <p class="mb-0 mt-2 font-italic">
            "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut. <a href="#" class="text-info">@consequat</a>"
          </p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer pt-3 mt-3 border-top">
            Someone famous in
            <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 col-mid">
      <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-html-view" data-id="Snippet">Preview{%- render 'icon-arrow-right' -%}</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-html-copy" data-id="Snippet">Copy {%- render 'icon-copy' -%}</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-right">
      <div id="htmlView-Snippet" class="html-view shadow html-view--widow">
        <blockquote class="blockquote blockquote-1 bg-white p-5 shadow rounded">
          <div class="blockquote-custom-icon bg-info shadow-sm"></div>
          <p class="mb-0 mt-2 font-italic">
            "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut. <a href="#" class="text-info">@consequat</a>"
          </p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer pt-3 mt-3 border-top">
            Someone famous in
            <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="htmlContent-Snippet" class="js-html-content d-none" data-id="Snippet">
  
      <blockquote class="blockquote blockquote-1 bg-white p-5 shadow rounded">
        <div class="blockquote-custom-icon bg-info shadow-sm"></div>
        <p class="mb-0 mt-2 font-italic">
          "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut. <a href="#" class="text-info">@consequat</a>"
        </p>
        <footer class="blockquote-footer pt-3 mt-3 border-top">
          Someone famous in
          <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
      
      <div class="quote-wrap text-center blockquote-2">
        <h4>Design Quality</h4>
        <div class="font-weight-light py-2 px-4">
          Rich and beautifully designed. There are countless features allowing for a great deal of flexibility in website creation. Logical and precise it's well thought out and works seamlessly as it should. The customer support is great too; timely, direct. I recommend.
        </div>
        <ul class="rating">
          <li class="rated">
          <li class="rated">
          <li class="rated">
          <li>
          <li>
        </ul>
        <div class="author-avatar">
          <img loading="lazy" width="auto" height="auto" class="lazyload" src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0092/7563/7839/files/ava_2_100x.png?v=1562226050">
        </div>
        <h6>Sky Walker</h6>
        <p>CEO</p>
      </div>
  
  
      <div class="service-media service-1 text-start">
        <span class="align-self-center mr-3 iconx4">
          [[ Icon ]]
        </span>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-2">Service heading</h5>
          Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis.
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-media service-2 text-center">
        <div class="media-body">
          <div class="mb-2 iconx4">
            [[ Icon ]]
          </div>
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-2">Service heading</h5>
          Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis.
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-media service-3 text-center">
        <div class="media-body">
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-2 text-theme">
            <span class="mr-1 iconx4">
              [[ Icon ]]
            </span>
            Service heading
          </h5>
          Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis.
        </div>
      </div>
  
  
  
      <div class="js-video" style="height:200px">
        <video loop="" onmouseover="this.play()" onmouseout="this.pause()">
          <source type="video/mp4" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0092/7563/7839/files/Videomenu.mp4?39752">
        </video>
      </div>
  
      <div class="card card-member-1">
        <div class="hv-image-brightness-n mb-3">
          <img loading="lazy" width="auto" height="auto" class="transition lazyload" src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0266/5745/6207/files/4.jpg?v=1567760858">
          <h4 class="pt-4 pb-2 m-0 font-family-2 px-3">Ajay Core</h4>
          <p class="px-3">CTO</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-member-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <p><img loading="lazy" width="auto" height="auto" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0092/7563/7839/files/2020.png?63177" alt="card image"></p>
            <h4 class="card-title">Sunlimetech</h4>
            <p class="card-text">This is basic card with image on top, title, description and button.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">[[Icon]]</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion accordion-1" id="accordion-{{ uniqueID }}">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header p-2">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
              <button class="btn btn--full" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne-{{ uniqueID }}" aria-expanded="true">
                ACCORDION TITLE 1
              </button>
            </h5>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseOne-{{ uniqueID }}" class="collapse show" data-parent="#accordion-{{ uniqueID }}">
            <div class="card-body">
              [[ CONTENT TEXT 1 ]]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header p-2">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
              <button class="btn btn--full collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo-{{ uniqueID }}" aria-expanded="false">
                ACCORDION TITLE 2
              </button>
            </h5>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseTwo-{{ uniqueID }}" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-{{ uniqueID }}">
            <div class="card-body">
              [[ CONTENT TEXT 2 ]]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header p-2">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
              <button class="btn btn--full collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree-{{ uniqueID }}" aria-expanded="false">
                ACCORDION TITLE 3
              </button>
            </h5>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseThree-{{ uniqueID }}" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-{{ uniqueID }}">
            <div class="card-body">
              [[ CONTENT TEXT 3 ]]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header p-2">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
              <button class="btn btn--full collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour-{{ uniqueID }}" aria-expanded="false">
                ACCORDION TITLE 4
              </button>
            </h5>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseFour-{{ uniqueID }}" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-{{ uniqueID }}">
            <div class="card-body">
              [[ CONTENT TEXT 4 ]]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr />